# Functional Features

The Human Development Index (HDI) Prediction System provides the following features:

## Home Page

* Displays an introduction to the Human Development Index.
* Allows users to navigate to the prediction page.

## Prediction Module

* Accepts the following user inputs:

  * Country
  * Life Expectancy
  * Expected Years of Schooling
  * Mean Years of Schooling
  * Gross National Income (GNI) per Capita
* Validates the entered values before prediction.

## Machine Learning Prediction

* Loads the trained Linear Regression model.
* Predicts the Human Development Index (HDI) score.

## Result Display

* Displays the predicted HDI score.
* Displays the Human Development category:

  * Very High Human Development
  * High Human Development
  * Medium Human Development
  * Low Human Development

## Deployment

* Integrated with a Flask web application.
* Successfully deployed using Render.
